        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In domini nostri Iehsu sit nomine Christi. Anno nativitate eius
                        millesimo centesimo nonagesimo secundo, indictione XI, ydus novembris.
                        Manifestus sum ego <persName><name ref="Gherarduccius"
                            >Gerarduccius</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Teminus"
                                >Temi</name></persName> quia per hanc cartulam (ve)ndo (…)
                                <persName><name ref="Aldricus">Alrigo</name></persName> quondam
                        dicti Temini videlicet medietatem integram pro indiviso unius <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montis</rs> positam in confinibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210"
                            key="#Mountains #Forests #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Roads"
                            >Putei</placeName> in loco ubi dicitur Cruce, cuius tenet unum caput in
                            <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, aliud in terra et <rs key="#Forests"
                            >bossco</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Clarectus">Chiarecti</name></persName>, latus in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Fornarius">Fornari</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hughicio">Uguicioni</name></persName>, aliud
                        vero latus in terra <persName><name ref="Wilielmus"
                            >Guilielmi</name></persName> quondam et <persName><name ref="Conciatus"
                                >Conciati</name></persName> et <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3213" key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">Sancti
                                Rolenthi</rs></orgName> et <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Ianni</name></persName>, habens in se <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Oil">olivas</rs> et <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">ficus</rs>.
                        (…) <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: sol. centum VIIII bonorum denariorum pisani
                        conii. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…). Actum in Montingnano,
                            <placeName ref="#places/63">Sancte Marie Montis</placeName>. Presentia
                        et testimonio <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Auderamus"
                            >Ayverami</name></persName> filius <persName><name ref="Greppaldus"
                                >Greppaldi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Aliccio">Aliccioni</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Romacus">Romachi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Bonaiutus">Bonaiuti</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandini</name></persName>.
                        Interfuerunt rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Item in presentia
                        suprascriptorum dictus Gerarduccius confitetur vendidisse cum patre suo
                        Teminio predicto Alrigo unam aliam petiolam terre in valle <placeName
                            ref="#places/3231">Lingnano</placeName>, tenens caput in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Bonincontrus">Bononcontri</name></persName>,
                        aliud in terra ecclesie Sancti Rolenthi, ambo latera in terris <persName
                            ref="#people/3217">Aldimari</persName>. Et confitetur de ea abuisse
                        pretium soldorum quinque et supena quadraginta soldorum promisit nullo
                        tempore litem neque modestiam (sic) facere suprascripto Arigo nec suo heredi
                        aut cui dederint. Prefatus Gerarduccius hanc cartulam fieri rogavit. (S) Ego
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Rubacastellus"
                                >Rubacastellus</name></persName> domni romanorum imperatoris <rs
                            key="#Judge">iudex ordinarius</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        hanc cartulam scripsi et dedi.</ab>
